OL,3,CArne Slot signs three year contract as
OL,4,CLiverpool's head coach
OL,6,FFormer Feyenoord coach Arne Slot has
OL,7,Fbeen officially confirmed as Jurgen
OL,8,FKlopp's successor at .
OL,10,FHowever, in a departure from
OL,11,Ftradition, the Dutchman will become
OL,12,Fthe club's first head coach rather
OL,13,Fthan manager.
OL,15,FIt is believed Slot has signed a three-
OL,16,Fyear contract and will officially take
OL,17,Fover on 1 June, subject to a work
OL,18,Fpermit.
