OL,3,CArne Slot signs three year contract as
OL,4,CLiverpool's head coach
OL,6,FIt has been an open secret for some
OL,7,Ftime, with Liverpool paying
OL,8,F#9.4million compensation to Feyenoord
OL,9,Fto secure his services and Slot
OL,10,Fconfirmed Anfield was his next
OL,11,Fdestination at his final pre-match
OL,12,Fpress conference at the Eredivisie
OL,13,Fclub on Friday.
OL,15,FLiverpool were keen to move swiftly to
OL,16,Freplace Klopp with a number of other
OL,17,Ftop European clubs also looking to
OL,18,Frecruit managers in what was seen as a
OL,19,F"challenging market" this summer.
