OL,6,FSlot was attractive to owners Fenway
OL,7,FSports Group (FSG) as they believe he
OL,8,Fhas demonstrated a reputation for over-
OL,9,Fperformance with AZ Alkmaar and
OL,10,FFeyenoord, being able to bring the
OL,11,Fbest out of players and has a clear
OL,12,Ffootballing identity, while also
OL,13,Fadopting an holistic and collegiate
OL,14,Fapproach which fits with their ethos.
