OL,3,CArne Slot signs three year contract as
OL,4,CLiverpool's head coach
OL,6,FHis job title of head coach means he
OL,7,Ffits into the new football structure
OL,8,Fwhich has had an overhaul in the last
OL,9,Ffew months with two former sporting
OL,10,Fdirectors ` Michael Edwards and Julian
OL,11,FWard ` returning to the fold as FSG's
OL,12,Fchief executive of football and
OL,13,Ftechnical director respectively.
OL,15,FNew sporting director Richard Hughes
OL,16,Fhas been recruited from Bournemouth
OL,17,Fand will officially begin work on 1
OL,18,FJune.
