OL,3,CArne Slot signs three year contract as
OL,4,CLiverpool's head coach
OL,6,FLiverpool's new manager will be
OL,7,Fexpected to be able to deliver more
OL,8,Fmemorable European nights at Anfield.
OL,10,FSlot would bring plenty of experience
OL,11,Fwith him. While at AZ, he took his
OL,12,Fside into the Europa League, where
OL,13,Fthey played Manchester United in 2019.
OL,15,FAfter moving to Feyenoord, Slot guided
OL,16,Fthe club to the Europa Conference
OL,17,FLeague final in May 2022. Eredivisie
OL,18,Fsuccess brought with it a crack at the
OL,19,FChampions League for 2023`24.
